data.description: RARE FIND! Country Elegance meets Convenience in this expansive property on over 5 gorgeous acres minutes from downtown Newnan. Turn onto the freshly paved Lane and up the azalea-lined horseshoe driveway and be transported to your 5000+ square foot respite with acres to roam! 5 Bedrooms, 3.5 baths, dual primary suites situated on lush landscaping & gardens with a hardwood canopy. Enter into the traditional foyer and find a light-filled living room with exposed beams and a white-washed brick fireplace. Double French Doors lead you into the sunroom, where you can step outside on the wrap-around porch for your morning coffee, or continue into the garden to cut some fresh flowers. The First Primary Suite resides on the main floor with double closets connecting to your Hilltop Home Office or guest space with a full bath. Upstairs, you will find the Second Primary Suite, 3 bedrooms each with sunlit views, and a huge Media Room, Play Room, or Living Space with another fireplace to keep cozy. Meticulous Owners have taken exceptional care of this space including adding Hydrofoil and Spray Foam insulation. Stubbed and Ready for a Bathroom/Kitchenette with its own parking and exterior entrance, your daylight basement will provide an extra 900 square feet of living space. This home was built on 16-inch centers (on rafters and floor joists) giving this home Stronger Bones than any new construction around! 3 Norma Lane, is a perfect 4 season home with land to garden, explore, or just enjoy your natural surroundings while still being convenient to Newnan, Peachtree City, I-85, Atlanta, and the Airport. NO HOA, ROOM TO PARK RV/BOAT! 1-Year Home Warranty Provided. PAINTING BUDGET of $2,000 PROVIDED! Meticulous Records of Upgrades. NO SIGN IN THE YARD.
